headline: Xcel Energy Third Quarter 2025 Earnings Report
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, October 30, 2025--Xcel Energy Inc. (NASDAQ: XEL) today reported 2025 third quarter GAAP earnings of $524 million, or $0.88 per share, compared with $682 million, or $1.21 per share in the same period in 2024 and ongoing earnings of $737 million, or $1.24 per share compared with $707 million or $1.25 per share in the same period in 2024. See Note 6 for reconciliation from GAAP to ongoing earnings.
